// add.su — calculator addition service.
//
// Reads operands "a" and "b" from the input axon and returns their
// sum on the real axis. Componentwise vector addition on real-axis
// numbers is exactly integer/float addition (docs/numeric-math.md):
// real(a + b) = real(a) + real(b). Exact through the kernel for
// operands within the float32 exact-integer range.
function vector on_axon(vector input_axon) {
    return axon_item(input_axon, "a") + axon_item(input_axon, "b");
}
